query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  SUM(CASE WHEN primary_image IS NOT NULL AND primary_image != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_images,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as unique_properties,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM property_images) as total_images
FROM properties p;
